Benjamin Busch https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Benjamin_Busch 0 Benjamin B. Busch is an American actor, writer, film maker, photographer, and United States Marine Corps Reserve officer. He is best known for his portrayal of Anthony Colicchio on the HBO original series The Wire.
